There is a fine line between loud music and unpleasant music my friend, and the  requirement of the loud notes to create the imagery you are talking is actually lacking. Music is best felt , when goes in a flow, loud or soft. The sudden onslaught is the only thing i felt was unnecessary. The rest of the song is really beautiful.
And just to talk about the extremities, I have an equally strong inclination towards rock music. So leave my taste to myself.
